CheapShark,is,a,service,that,tracks,the,prices,of,PC,games,on,sites,like,Amazon,Steam,and,GamersGate,and,shows,shoppers,the,best,deals,Through,the,site,users,can,look,up,top,deals,search,for,the,best,price,on,a,specific,game,sign,up,for,alerts,or,simply,browse,what,s,available,The,CheapShark,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,the,site,s,pricing,data,into,their,own,websites,or,applications